# VENTION-SDLC-MANAGED:BEGIN v=0.0.1
#
# Everything between BEGIN / END is framework-managed and rewritten on every
# `vsdlc install`. Add your team's ignore rules OUTSIDE these markers — they
# will be preserved byte-for-byte across upgrades.
#
# --- per-developer state (R3 — never committed) -------------------------
/.vsdlc/workspace.local.toml
/.vsdlc/telemetry/
/.vsdlc/.lock
/.mcp.json
/.mise.toml
# --- framework-owned IDE config (R10 watched paths) ---------------------
/.claude/
/.cursor/
/.codex/
/.gemini/
/.github/hooks/
/.agents/
/.vsdlc/scripts/
# --- BMAD module workspace (with allow-list overrides) ------------------
/_bmad/*
!/_bmad/custom/
!/_bmad/custom/*.toml
/_bmad/custom/*.user.toml
/_bmad/custom/config.yaml
/_bmad-vention/
/_bmad-output/.cache/
/_bmad-output/**/*.lock
/.playwright-cli/
# --- scratch / OS noise -------------------------------------------------
*.log
.DS_Store
*.tmp
*.bak
# VENTION-SDLC-MANAGED:END
